name: Hyperesthesia
description:
"My body is a cage..."

Have you ever suffered from migraine? Or have tried some lysergic stuff? Have you ever tried to push back the sleep as far as possible? Then you know what I'm talking about.

The third drop of the "extreme doodling" series ; I'm so chaotic that I didn't even precise it in the description of "Stomp" and "Monikon Partitiivi".

A freehand drawing, still grotesque, toony and psychedelic. 


Black pen on white paper.
